Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上原睦月  水瓶座  B型血  身高155cm
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座右铭是「向前冲！」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫藤芽生  金牛座  A型血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我不太喜欢这种名堂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明喜欢的不得了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稻森光香  在学生会担任书记
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩羯座  A型血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢的话语是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桃  停下来停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重来一次  重来一次啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是  做宣传的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙  什么时候拍下来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是稻森光香  在学生会担任书记
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢的话语是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.43,0:16:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢的话语是「朋…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:16:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「朋友」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.38,0:17:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「朋友」…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉  因为播放时发生了一些故障
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来将重新播放新的校歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点…  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  请各位欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要像这样一事无成就和大家分开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚的是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.39,0:17:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是这首比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  重新听过之后觉得原来的也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还待在这里好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还待在这里真的好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.74,0:18:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  这么胡来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学美～～！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.12,0:19:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把学园祭办下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和最最重要的伙伴们一起做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  把学园祭办下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  此刻  做只有我们才能做到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然被蜜柑教育了  真是伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向前…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.23,0:20:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请签个名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.07,0:20:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请签个名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  拜托了……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.08,0:21:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是白费工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想改变学校却无法实现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我想那并不是白费工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候一起坚守学生宿舍的伙伴们的名字和长相
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.62,0:21:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都记得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.66,0:21:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…你看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  没有人愿意签名  还是老样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就认输了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.68,0:21:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别泄气  别泄气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有泄气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以签名吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.04,0:22:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距学园祭复活署名裁决日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有46小时
